en:
Y'ALL BEST NOT HAVE <w><c=banana>SLAMMED</c></w> THE
GROUND!
IT'S REAL FRAGILE, I TELL YA!
APPRECIATE THE WAKE UP CALL, THOUGH!

TURNS OUT <c=violastro>VIOLASTRO'S</c> GOT MORE
IMPORTANT BUSINESS TO DEAL WITH THAN
Y'ALL SHODDY ADVENTURERS!

IN FACT, HE AIN'T EVEN ON THIS PLANET NO
MORE, BWEHEHE!
I WASN'T SUPPOSED TO TELL Y'ALL THAT!

NO MATTER!
Y'ALL'S TIME IS NIGH!
